    <td><p> <strong>Pro Se Assistance Form M-2</strong></p>
        <p>Form M-2 is designed to capture general information and assistance provided to people wishing to handle simple legal matters themselves without extensive assistance from an attorney.  This may include ìhelp desk at courtî or ìworkshops or clinicsî among others. Refer to Pro Se Assistance Form M-2 for the various categories included. </p>
        <p>In the Measured field, please enter the number of other services cases that you are able to count. In the Estimated field, please enter any additional other services that you have not counted, but have estimated on a reasonable basis. The total field is a calculated field that adds up the measured and estimated figures. </p>        
        <p>Downloads - Form M-2, Item 3 (was item 4): this category should capture situations where users obtained a copy of the item on the Web for their use. Since this is its purpose, printing of a Web item will also be counted as a download, although, strictly speaking, it is not an actual ìdownload.î ù</p>
     </td>
  </tr>
</table>
