    <td><p><strong>Referred  </strong><strong>Form M-3</strong></p>
      <p>In Form M-3, please report referrals that do not qualify as ìcasesî - i.e. any referral in which no actual legal advice or other legal service is provided directly to the client. See Referred M-3 for the various categories included in this form. </p>
      <p>In the Measured field please enter the number of other services that you are able to count. In the Estimated field, please enter any additional other services that you have not counted but have estimated on a reasonable basis. The total field is a calculated field that adds up the measured and estimated figures. </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
